						<span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium border border-gray-100 group-[.bg-black]:bg-[#222] group-[.bg-black]:text-gray-300 group-[.bg-black]:border-[#333]">Tailwind CSS</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-gray-50 text-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium border border-gray-100 group-[.bg-black]:bg-[#222] group-[.bg-black]:text-gray-300 group-[.bg-black]:border-[#333]">Twig</span>
